    "Name": "Harpy",
    "Details": "Designed as a long range sniper VTOL by Brigadier Corporation, the Harpy debuted in 3065. Poor sales and an odd weapons array resulted in the design ceasing production after the Jihad and numbers would dwindle to near extinction during the Dark Age. A 30 ton VTOL, the Harpy is powered by a 40 rated fusion engine and armed with an ER large Laser, a UAC/2 and a Small Laser.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 6/9 hexes / 180/270 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       125     15\n<b>Left</b>          95     15\n<b>Right</b>        95     15\n<b>Rear</b>         75     15\n\n<b>Total</b>      405     75</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Long</color>",
